/features/details.content:
# Details

Details shortcode is a helper for `details` html5 element. It is going to replace `expand` shortcode.

## Example
```tpl
{{</* details "Title" [open] */>}}
## Markdown content
Lorem markdownum insigne...
{{</* /details */>}}
```
```tpl
{{</* details title="Title" open=true */>}}
## Markdown content
Lorem markdownum insigne...
{{</* /details */>}}
```

